&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in Telecommunications or Data Centre related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In depth knowledge of Telecom structured cabling standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In depth knowledge of network device / server deployment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In depth knowledge of DCO standards and operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years use of industry standard test equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective organizational skills and high attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building Management System and Branch Circuit Monitoring experience&lt;/li

